1. Convert uppercase character to lowercase

        for(char ch='A'; ch <= 'Z'; ch++)
            ch | ' '

2. Convert lowercase character to uppercase

        for(char ch='a'; ch <= 'z'; ch++)
            ch & '_'

3. Invert alphabet

        for(char ch='a'; ch <= 'z'; ch++)
            ch ^ ' '

        for(char ch='A'; ch <= 'Z'; ch++)
            ch ^ ' '

4. Find letter's position in alphabet

        A & 31
        c & 31

